
[HOW TO BUILD]

Edit the Makefile and set PREFIX and BINDIR, and type make xxx as follows:

$ make boot
$ make iraf
$ make reboot
$ make tables
$ make noao

[HOW TO INSTALL]

$ su
# make install         (analysis environment only)
# make install_devel   (development environment only)

You can use DESTDIR=... to make your IRAF packages:

# make install DESTDIR=rootdir
# make install_devel DESTDIR=rootdir

